Rota Portmaster Release (https://www.portmaster.games) 
=========================

Original version by:
https://github.com/HarmonyHoney/ROTA

Portmaster Version: 	

- Cebion https://github.com/Cebion
	
Special thanks to: tekkenfede for helping with godot config files

To compile:
===========

wget https://downloads.tuxfamily.org/godotengine/3.5/godot-3.5-stable.tar.xz
tar xf godot-3.5-stable.tar.xz
cd godot-3.5-stable/platform
git clone https://github.com/Cebion/frt.git
cd ../
scons platform=frt tools=no target=release use_llvm=yes module_webm_enabled=no -j12
strip bin/godot.frt.opt.llvm

Instructions:
=============

To run the game start Rota.sh from your ports folder.


Controls:
=============

A			= Jump / Enter
B			= Back / Cancel
DPAD	    = Move Character